==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intrusionist
<hw>In*tru"sion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who intrudes;
especially, one who favors the appointment of a clergyman to a parish,
by a patron, against the wishes of the parishioners.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intrusive</ent>⟦br⟧
